quotes.quote: A moment's beginning ends in a moment
The future can never lie about the past. In the end, you will see the beginning.
Don't be afraid of an endless road, but the road with an end!
Everything is going to be fine in the end. If it's not, it's not the end.
All stories end when they have returned to their beginnings.
The end justifies the means. Sometimes you have to do the wrong thing to get the right result.
Happiness is not the victory, success or accomplishment; it is what happens at the end of the day?
In the end, the world returns to a grain.
End is not the End, in fact, E.N.D means "Effort Never Dies".
The truest end of life is to know the life that never ends.
In the end, all or nothing will matter
In the end, it's not the years in your life that count. It's the life in your years.
But if there must be an end, let it be loud. Let it be bloody. Better to burn than to wither away in the dark.
You are the end of beauty and creativity one must have created so far.
We are past the end of things now, but I don't want to leave.
Life's just a bunch of accidents, connected by one perfect end.
An endless path is frightening but the path that ends is even more frightening!
But what if all the tranquility, all the comfort, all the contentment were now to come to a horrifying end?
It is good to have an end to journey towards; but it is the journey that matters, in the end.
Sometimes there is no solution. Sometimes there's simply an end.
There is an end to every journey.
Our lives begin to end the day we become silent about things that matter.
When we are at the end of life, to die means to go away; when we are at the beginning, to go away means to die.
The end always doesn't justify the means you used to reach there.
Sometimes things are most beautiful when they're coming to an end.
It's not the end of the physical body that should worry us. Rather our concern must be to live while we're alive.
The end is the best part of any story
Beginning in itself has no value, it is an end which makes beginning meaningful, we must end what we begun.
Those who don't want to take risks in life end up been the losers.
In the End, we will remember not the words of our enemies, but the silence of our friends.
